<bibRefCitation author="Fric, A. V." box="[688,849,950,976]" pageId="9" pageNumber="162" refId="ref8346" refString="Fric, A. V. (1928) Cacti the coming fashion - pricelist for 1928." type="journal volume" year="1928">Fric (1928: 3)</bibRefCitation>
